            <h1>Stay at Affordable Accommodations in Central London</h1>
            <p>Planning a trip to London for your holiday or for business means knowing not only where the best part of the city is to stay but where rooms are that fit nicely into your budget. Central London can be the best place to stay since it is so close to many great attractions and business areas but it can also be difficult to find accommodations that are clean, comfortable and affordable for you. If you are looking for cheap and budget hotels in Paddington, the Paddington Hotel London offers everything you need.</p>
            <br>
            <h2 class="caps black">Location</h2>
            <p><iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2482.984785770372!2d-0.18006108411215935!3d51.513495118078396!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x48760552c21a3a41%3A0x5f2a5e5bdb24dace!2sPaddington+Hotel+London+%E2%80%93+Hotels+in+Paddington+Central+London!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1463140134432" width="100%" height="160" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
           </div>
            <div class="grid-7 grid bg2">
            	<div class="copy">
                <h2><img src="images/img1.jpg" alt="Cheap Hotels in Paddington - The Paddington Hotel London" class="blouquote-left">London Accommodation</h2>
                <p>When you stay at this hotel you will be in one of the best areas of the city. You will find easy access to some of the best tourist attractions found in the city, such as Buckingham Palace, Madame Tussauds, Hyde Park, Westminster Abbey and much more. The hotel resides very close to the Paddington Station so you have easy access to public transportation, making it very simple for you to get around the areas of London.</p>
                
                <div class="box1">
                <h2>Amenities <img src="images/img2.jpg" alt=" Bed And Breakfast Accommodation in Paddington" class="blouquote-right"></h2>
                <p>A stay at the Paddington Hotel London provides you with a stay at one of the great bed and breakfast hotels near Paddington Station London. You have access to all of the essentials you need in a hotel, from comfortable bedding, private bathroom facilities, refrigerator, coffee and tea maker, television and more. You will also get popular amenities such as free Wi-Fi in public areas of the hotel and a safe in your room to go along with the complimentary continental breakfast that is available each morning to help start your day.</p>
                </div>
                <br><br>
                <h2><img src="images/img3.jpg" alt="Budget Hotels Paddington - The Paddington Hotel London" class="blouquote-left">The Right Price</h2>
                <p>Perhaps the best feature you will find regarding the Paddington Hotel London is that it is the most affordable accommodation in Central London. The room rates available will fit nicely into any type of budget you may have. Whether you are planning to stay for just one night in the city or have a whole week planned for business meetings or sightseeing, you will find that the rooms available meet all of your needs and are ideal for your wallet. You can even take advantage of special promotions or booking online to get the best rates possible.</p>
                <p>For a hotel in the best part of London at the best price you can find, make your reservations at the Paddington Hotel London. You will be glad you chose this quaint, Victorian building for your stay and will be happy with all it has to offer you.</p>
                </div>
